Version 0.3
===========
	- Minor code-cleanups
	- Documented and parameterized certain mechanism (anti-DOS,
	  vector-resizing, sliding random MACs); see src/parameters.h for
	  details
	- BUGFIX: fixed broken signal-handling with dietlibc (dietlibc sets
	  SIG_DFL handler when entering a handler and -- in opposite to
	  glibc-2.3.1 -- does not restore this value to the handler set with
	  signal())
	- BUGFIX: fixed stupid typo in vector-resize code which caused
	  excessive memory-consumption

Version 0.2
===========
	- build-fixes with RH 6.2
	- minor build-fixes
	- documentation was added

Version 0.1
===========
	- initial release
